history.text: This movie seems exciting, what are your thoughts?
It seems a bit outlandish, I don't normally watch scientific movies. What made you approach this movie to watch?

Honestly, I am not a big fan of scientific movies as well. I recognized the actor right away so it caught my attention. I like how critics claim DiCaprio as "never been better." That made me want to watch it also.
I more or less just wanted to see Joseph Gordon-Levtit preform since he's a great supporting actor.
Did you like any parts of the story?
Yes, indeed! I do like how the story line seems suspenseful. I enjoy suspense or movies that keep you guessing.
Did the rating bring you any concerns?
The ratings seemed fairly high so I came into it thinking the movie would be a real bluckbuster but it was lackluster for me.
I did really enjoy the use of mazes in the story, cause the mind is like one big maze
